                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200217-10-off55 t18200217-10-cd56"></join>, six handkerchiefs, value 1 l. 5 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18200217-10-victim141" type="victimName">
                     George 
